The paper presents a novel unsupervised model for graph embedding and classification, which involves the use of self-attention and recurrent transition. This work is related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, specifically in the area of graph representation learning and classification. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
